<bibRefCitation author="Quero" pageId="16" pageNumber="25" refString="Quero, J. C., Hureau, J. C., Karrer, C., Post, A. &amp; Saldanha, L. (1990) Check-list of the fishes of the eastern tropical Atlantic. 3 volumes. Lisbon." type="book chapter" year="1990">
Quéro 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">et al.</emphasis>
(
<number box="[200,264,1896,1922]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1990.0">1990</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number box="[278,326,1896,1922]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="898.0">898</number>
), even though the species is common there. Recorded from Madeira by, for instance, 
<bibRefCitation author="Wirtz" pageId="16" pageNumber="26" refString="Wirtz, P. (1994) Unterwasserfuhrer Madeira, Kanaren, Azoren: Fische - Underwater Guide Madeira, Canary Islands, Azores: Fish. Naglschmid Verlag, Stuttgart." type="book" year="1994">
Wirtz (
<number box="[160,224,1936,1962]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1994.0">1994</number>
: 
<number box="[235,281,1936,1962]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="110.0">110</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, with a colour photo from Madeira.
</paragraph>
